BT /F1 12 Tf 72 760 Td
(SPI_Slave Verification and RTL2GDS Flow) Tj
T*
(Koen Van Caekenberghe, ChipDesign B.V., June 2026) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Overview) Tj
T*
(The SPI_Slave design is a small SPI slave IP block that supports a simple 8-bit) Tj
T*
(address and data transfer protocol. The SPI interface operates in mode 0) Tj
T*
(\(CPOL=0, CPHA=0\). The design exposes a secondary read port `Data2_out` to) Tj
T*
(allow local readback of register contents.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Design Summary) Tj
T*
(The RTL implements the following functionality:) Tj
T*
(- SPI command and data phases with a 1-byte command word.) Tj
T*
(- Read/write selection using the MSB of the command byte.) Tj
T*
(- Eight 8-bit internal registers \(Register0..Register7\).) Tj
T*
(- Synchronous register update on the internal clock domain.) Tj
T*
(- MISO output generation during SPI read transactions.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Top-level interface:) Tj
T*
(- Clk -- internal clock input.) Tj
T*
(- iRST_N -- active-low reset.) Tj
T*
(- SCK, MOSI, SSEL -- SPI inputs.) Tj
T*
(- MISO -- SPI output.) Tj
T*
(- Add2_in, Data2_out -- local read address and data output.) Tj
T*
(- debug -- internal debug status outputs.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Place-and-Route Flow) Tj
T*
(The repository includes a LibreLane-based RTL2GDS flow configured for the) Tj
T*
(IHP SG13G2 PDK.) Tj
T*
(Important flow files: flow/Makefile, flow/config.yaml, flow/run_flow.sh,) Tj
T*
(flow/ihp_pdk.env.example, flow/constraint.sdc, flow/place_route.tcl.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Verification Approach) Tj
T*
(Two testbenches are provided:) Tj
T*
(- tb_spi_slave.v -- original RTL testbench.) Tj
T*
(- tb_spi_slave_compare.v -- comparison testbench that can instantiate either) Tj
T*
(  RTL or synthesized netlists using the SYNTH macro.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Back-to-Back Results) Tj
T*
(RTL simulation result: FINISH 750: addr=03 data=0d debug=1b miso=1 ssel=0) Tj
T*
(Synthesized netlist result: FINISH 750: addr=03 data=0d debug=1b miso=1 ssel=0) Tj
T*
(Final gate-level netlist result with SG13G2 library:) Tj
T*
(FINISH 75000: addr=03 data=0d debug=1b miso=1 ssel=0) Tj
T*
(The final gate-level simulation matches the RTL and synthesized netlists on) Tj
T*
(observable outputs. The different finish time is due to the gate-level) Tj
T*
(library timescale.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Reproduction Instructions) Tj
T*
(Run the flow from flow/ with ./run_flow.sh after configuring flow/ihp_pdk.env.) Tj
T*
(Run RTL and synthesized verification with tb_spi_slave_compare.v as described) Tj
T*
(in the README.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Conclusion) Tj
T*
(The SPI_Slave design is functionally consistent across RTL, synthesized netlist,) Tj
T*
(and final gate-level netlist simulations. The repository includes the) Tj
T*
(necessary sources, flow files, and verification bench to rerun the flow.) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
